			All Rights Reserved | 
			<a href="#">Terms of Use</a> and <a href="#">Privacy Policy</a> | 
			<a href="#">Help</a> and <a href="#">Feedback</a> |
			Updated Jan. 30, 2009
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
